params.812: Reach level 20 in the Attack skill.
params.813: Ensure your combat style is set to provide Attack XP. The Barbarians south of Edgeville are suitable targets to fight.
params.814: The Barbarians south of Edgeville are suitable targets to fight.|To get to Barbarian Village, travel north to Varrock then travel West, use the world map to navigate if you get lost.|Watch out for Gunthor the Brave!|Visit the Stronghold of Security while you are there for additional rewards, more variety in monsters and to learn how to keep your account secure.
params.823: Barbarians can be found in their village, especially in the pub.
